## Installation & Setup

1. Clone the repository

git clone https://github.com/Maheshvadhiya/traffic-signal-management.git

2. Navigate into the project folder

cd traffic-signal-management

##  Start Development Server

```bash
npx expo start 
```

### Step 5 — Open the App

| Method | Command / Action |
|--------|-----------------|
| Android Emulator | Press `a` in terminal |
| iOS Simulator (macOS only) | Press `i` in terminal |
| Physical Android device | Scan QR code with **Expo Go** app |
| Physical iPhone | Scan QR code with **Expo Go** app |
| Web browser | Press `w` in terminal |

